name: Sofia - Hotel Booking App UI Kit(Excellent)
description:
Sofia - Hotel Booking App UI Kit(Excellent)

Sofia is an aesthetic, rich and modern travel and hotel booking app UI kit specially designed to fit right into the new iOS, iPhone & all mobile devices.

Sofia comes with a set of 56 beautifully designed screens; available in dark and light. Sofia is highly customizable, well layered, 100% vector and organized.

Features

– 52 screens, +200 elements and icons

– Available with dark and light modes

– Highly customizable designs

– 100% vector and organized layers

– Screen resolution (375x812px)

– Symbols available for Sketch

– Works in Figma, Sketch, Photoshop and XD
